<H3> <TI>   Dialogue With FIS; Unity of Army Questioned </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Dialogue With FIS; Unity of Army Questioned </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94AF0145B Algiers EL WATAN in French 19 Mar 94 p 1 </F>
