<H3> <TI>   `Schutzjuden' Status for Israelis Anticipated </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Schutzjuden' Status for Israelis Anticipated </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94AA0055B Tel Aviv HAYARDEN in Hebrew 28 Feb 94 p 
