<H3> <TI>   Tourism Minister Announces Removal of Hurdles </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Tourism Minister Announces Removal of Hurdles </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94AS0235K Madras THE HINDU in English 8 Mar 94 p 16 </F>
