<H3> <TI>   Limited Role for Foreigners in Private Banks Planned </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Limited Role for Foreigners in Private Banks Planned </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94AS0235B Madras THE HINDU in English 8 Mar 94 p 14 </F>
<F P=103> 94AS0235B </F>
<F P=104>  Madras THE HINDU </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
