<H3> <TI>   Foreign Investors Offered Preferential Shares </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Investors Offered Preferential Shares </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94AS0233B Madras THE HINDU (International Edition) in 
English 5 Mar 94 p 14 </F>

<F P=103> 94AS0233B </F>
<F P=104>  Madras THE HINDU (International Edition) </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


