<H3> <TI>   Opposition on Price Hike: Parliament Was Ignored </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Opposition on Price Hike: Parliament Was Ignored </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94AS0233A Madras THE HINDU (International Edition) in 
