<F P=106> ["Nuclear forces to get pride of place in development of </F>
Russian armed forces - Grachev" -- RIA headline] 
  [Text] Moscow, March 16, RIA -- Defence Minister Pavel 
Grachev, speaking at a news briefing today, said that in the 
present conditions it is strategic nuclear forces that are 
Russia's real guarantee of security, which is stated in the 
Russian military doctrine. 

