<H3> <TI>   Talks on Payments for Nuclear Weapons Held With Russia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Talks on Payments for Nuclear Weapons Held With Russia </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS1803151694 Minsk BELAPAN in Belarusian 1305 GMT 18 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> WS1803151694 </F>
<F P=104>  Minsk BELAPAN </F>
<F P=105>  Belarusian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] As a BELAPAN correspondent has learned at the 
Belarusian Foreign Ministry, Russian-Belarusian negotiations on 
cooperation and payments for recycling the strategic nuclear 
weapons that are currently being withdrawn from Belarus have 
recently been held in Moscow. Appropriate international 
agreements have been drafted. 

</TEXT>

